      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "良かったら……もし本当に差し支えなければ\nなんですけど……膨らませてくれませんか？",
      "startTime": 18.8000006994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
