      "text": "わさび入りシロップなんて使ってませんよ～？\n疑うならこころがほら……むぐむぐ。おいし～",
      "startTime": 130.1666673661,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_02-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "これで安心しましたよね？　はい、こっちのイチゴ味を\nどうぞ～。毒味しましょうか？",
      "startTime": 141.5898673312,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.9073886259
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "いや、疑って悪かったな。いただきます……\nむ……ぐぐっ！？　けほっ、これ……タバスコか！？",
      "startTime": 149.9333340328,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.0165449166
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_02-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "ふっふっふ、油断しましたね！　こころが食べていない\n方のかき氷を差し出した時点で疑うべきでしたね～",
      "startTime": 159.9999956132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_02-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "生き馬の目を抜くアイドル業界で、これだけの人気\nグループを抱えながら疑うことを知らないとは……",
      "startTime": 167.6878369673,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 171.4272020046
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_02-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんはまだまだですね～",
      "startTime": 171.4272020046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 179.8333289465
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "すまない、辛過ぎて話が全然頭に入らなかった……\nもう一回言ってくれるか？",
      "startTime": 179.8333289465,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_02-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "くっ、タバスコをたっぷり入れたのが\n裏目に出てしまいました……！",
      "startTime": 185.3333289465,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_spa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3631.2948091999997,
          "startTime": 188.9646237557
        }
      ]
    },
